<ApiTester {endpoint}>

# Event

Track in-progress player actions during a round. This is useful for resuming gameplay if a player disconnects mid-round - the recorded events allow the frontend to reconstruct the round state.

<Callout type="info">

Events are associated with the player's current active round. A valid session must be established via the <a href="/docs/api/authenticate">Authenticate</a> endpoint, and a round must be in progress via the <a href="/docs/api/play">Play</a> endpoint.

</Callout>

